yTime":"2020-03-21T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎患者痛苦死亡過程曝光　前線醫生：本質如同浸死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1888360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1888360</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f1628016fed221ef8a4c3a0309739352bc8d1176","tid":1936042,"uid":223428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"141eda3403b529ec448692fdf58e547927ae1030","tid":1936042,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"666ae35ebe123b9d4f0ec0806f411fdd1b3b0401","tid":1936042,"uid":50719,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:58:18.000Z","msg":"似漫漫浸死，不過浸死你既係你自己d鼻涕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"點解係鼻涕？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:05:03.000Z","msg":"d黏液塞滿你的肺泡"},{"pid":"4e5961ce86e4dcd5cbee178f1b508cddb150bf2c","tid":1936042,"uid":17232,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ba8bd05f2a6b2f1c0fff6c10738caf2a1e54c41b","tid":1936042,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎患者痛苦死亡過程曝光　前線醫生：本質如同浸死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1888360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1888360</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:09:37.000Z","msg":"該名前線醫生在文中詳細描述患者死前感受，<br />\n<br />\n一直呼吸困難，直到最後幾分鐘，病人全程清醒，病人會呼救，會哭著喊著說醫生你救救我&hellip;&hellip;伴隨著劇烈地掙扎，直到呼出最後一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根據該帖文，新冠肺炎重症病人死亡前的3個步痛苦過程分別是漸進式窒息、痛苦爭扎、慘叫身亡。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n該醫生甚至直指，「死因本質上和淹死一個道理」，「大量的水，進到了肺裡面之後，氧進不去，肺被病毒導致的果凍狀的分泌物給佔滿了，換氣功能完全喪失，再濃的氧也進不去血裡面；而吸痰也沒用，因為靠氣管鏡到達不了那個終末端的地方」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845b2dde738918526aa220472ea21c799cea97e5","tid":1936042,"uid":273576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd60352c2358a28841eabae4f4ff1931c0db113d","tid":1936042,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0eb9d8e67b9e92eb8b20de587803a7dfc751953e","tid":1936042,"uid":273576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"都係死既感覺，實有機會試一次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:01:21.000Z","msg":"你浸死同跳樓死感覺都唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"一樣的 ,唔通只係死前既感覺"},{"pid":"951f35032c59b4906d7b6fab38510676942abb8d","tid":1936042,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"你當係不斷呼吸都呼吸唔到 自然會氣勢咁大力呼吸 但係都唔夠 要再大力 之後不斷既咳 個腦慢慢唔夠氧氣 身體開始抽畜 最後死個下應該係封喉斷氣"},{"pid":"2683d78f71c5b87a2baf82cffc5b6cce9c4ab780","tid":1936042,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"845b2dde738918526aa220472ea21c799cea97e5","tid":1936042,"uid":273576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd60352c2358a28841eabae4f4ff1931c0db113d","tid":1936042,"uid":17232,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0eb9d8e67b9e92eb8b20de587803a7dfc751953e","tid":1936042,"uid":273576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"都係死既感覺，實有機會試一次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:01:21.000Z","msg":"你浸死同跳樓死感覺都唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"一樣的 ,唔通只係死前既感覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思講得唔好 係問臨死前咩感覺"},{"pid":"e79a182d09fc425d24a87bb62f380ff6f07b7d5e","tid":1936042,"uid":17232,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"951f35032c59b4906d7b6fab38510676942abb8d","tid":1936042,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"你當係不斷呼吸都呼吸唔到 自然會氣勢咁大力呼吸 但係都唔夠 要再大力 之後不斷既咳 個腦慢慢唔夠氧氣 身體開始抽畜 最後死個下應該係封喉斷氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"見到全世界咁多人死 我地睇落好似只係一個數字<br />\n但係其實每個死嘅人背後其實都經歷左咁痛苦嘅死法<br />\n無人覺得好恐怖？"},{"pid":"ef183d61e5755a3d5a7e2493aadf327a667b1419","tid":1936042,"uid":253773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以confirm救唔撚到恐前打支勁麻醉針，等個病人舒服啲"},{"pid":"a0a11c18d979c529cc61591cf1ae8df071c3f168","tid":1936042,"uid":311611,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n窒息式性愛（英語：erotic asphyxiation、breath control play）是指為了獲得性快感，故意限制大腦供氧的行為。該做法利用人體在<span style=\"color: red;\">缺氧、窒息的瞬間</span>，局部器官的高度收縮，而使自己或對方從中得到性快感和性高潮，但常有不小心而令人死亡的事件發生。如果是自慰時進行此行為，則會被稱為自慰性窒息（英語：autoerotic asphyxiation）。在美國精神醫學學會的《精神疾病診斷與統計手冊》中，窒息式性愛被歸於性偏離的一種。<br />\n<br />\n自慰性窒息從17世紀便有所記載，起先是用來治療勃起功能障礙的。[4]這種療法很可能源自被絞刑者，人們注意到男性受刑者出現了勃起的現象，有時能<span style=\"color: red;\">夠持續到死亡之後（即死亡勃起），偶爾亦會伴有射精</span>。[5]"},{"pid":"aac869cae43b44cc94ae71eb13d5ab1bc5228f57","tid":1936042,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e79a182d09fc425d24a87bb62f380ff6f07b7d5e","tid":1936042,"uid":17232,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"951f35032c59b4906d7b6fab38510676942abb8d","tid":1936042,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"你當係不斷呼吸都呼吸唔到 自然會氣勢咁大力呼吸 但係都唔夠 要再大力 之後不斷既咳 個腦慢慢唔夠氧氣 身體開始抽畜 最後死個下應該係封喉斷氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"見到全世界咁多人死 我地睇落好似只係一個數字<br />\n但係其實每個死嘅人背後其實都經歷左咁痛苦嘅死法<br />\n無人覺得好恐怖？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9382dbf6e90f3a4493097d4e27b9f5bccb035141","tid":1936042,